OL,3,C10k organisers investigating after
OL,4,Crunners complain course was too short
OL,6,FOrganisers are investigating the
OL,7,Flength of this year's Derby 10k amid
OL,8,Ffears the route was too short.
OL,10,FRunners competing in the race across
OL,11,Fthe city, held today (Sunday, March
OL,12,F15), have complained that the route
OL,13,Fwasn't actually 10 kilometres long.
OL,15,FOrganisers have now begun a review
OL,16,Finto the event and concerns over the
OL,17,Frun's distance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
