OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773648268
OL,3,C10k organisers investigating after
OL,4,Crunners complain course was too short
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Derby County
OL,7,FCommunity Trust said: "We acknowledge
OL,8,Fand appreciate the feedback that
OL,9,Ftoday's route may have been short in
OL,10,Fdistance.
OL,12,F"The course was run on an officially
OL,13,Fmeasured route.
OL,15,F"However, we take these concerns
OL,16,Fseriously and will be reviewing the
OL,17,Fmatter as a priority with the
OL,18,FAssociation of UK Course Measurers.
OL,20,F"We will provide a further update once
OL,21,Fthis review has been completed."
